sci_fi_thriller.title: Sci-Fi Thriller
sci_fi_thriller.description: Extraterrestrial lifeforms, alien worlds, time travel and more. These movies always have another puzzle to unlock.

284009.title: Turbulent Skies
284009.description: A pilot-less plane malfunctions midflight, and the military threatens to destroy it before it crashes—but the one man who can fix it is on the ground.

289797.title: The Divide
289797.description: Survivors of a nuclear attack endure days in a basement, only to be driven mad by dwindling supplies and fear of what lies outside their bunker.

314137.title: APP
314137.description: After a night of partying in the dorms, Anna wakes up to find that a new app on her phone. Initially helpful and clever, IRIS soon begins behaving in cruel, mysterious ways.

316459.title: Cube
316459.description: Seven strangers find themselves imprisoned in a seemingly endless maze filled with deadly traps and must fight to escape,  despite the odds.

321859.title: Enter Nowhere
321859.description: In this bizarre thriller, different timelines intersect when three strangers unexpectedly arrive at a cabin in the woods and are unable to leave.

327005.title: Aimy in a Cage
327005.description: A creative teenage girl is placed into a mind-altering procedure to civilise her, while news of a virus epidemic spreads throughout the world.

341531.title: Nightmare Code
341531.description: Nightmare Code is an independent sci-fi thriller about behavior recognition technology, behavior modification, 24/7 surveillance and artificial intelligence.

342032.title: 10.0 Earthquake
342032.description: As a series of earthquakes tear apart LA, Emily and Jason race through the ruined city, diverting the epicenter, in hopes of saving millions of lives.

357489.title: CO2
357489.description: A mysterious deadly vapor suffocates a small American coal town. Based on actual events.

364445.title: Area Q
364445.description: An investigative journalist whose world is turned upside-down when his son disappears is sent to Brazil to investigate close encounter sightings.

367633.title: 500 MPH Storm
367633.description: In this tale of man vs. nature, one man must save his family after an experiment gone wrong unleashes deadly hurricanes capable of destroying America.

367793.title: Megafault
367793.description: After a mining explosion causes a massive earthquake, it’s up to a miner and a seismologist to save the U.S. from further destruction.

396740.title: The Frame
396740.description: Two strangers find their lives collide in an impossible way. Taking on the very root of fate, destiny, and their own existence, Alex and Sam race through an ever-changing universe while being pursued by a demonic man determined to erase the world.

403311.title: B4
403311.description: Three friends find themselves trapped in an underground parking garage with doorways leading into the past and future and floors that repeat themselves for eternity. They must struggle to keep their sanity, if not their lives.

454193.title: Emulation
454193.description: A corporation allows a man to live life through a movie, where he is soon framed for murder and marked for death through a nationwide man hunt.

456859.title: Control
456859.description: A morally deviant inmate on death row agrees to be a test subject for a new behavior modification drug in order to get a second chance at life.

457150.title: The Cure
457150.description: A medical researcher discovers that cancer is too profitable to be cured. Caught in a vast and sinister conspiracy, she begins the fight for her life.

463151.title: Implanted
463151.description: When Ethan (Justice Leak) begins to experience flashes of disjointed and bewildering memories he desperately attempts to put together the pieces of his life, but is he prepared for the truth?

468437.title: Beta Test
468437.description: A champion gamer finds events in a new video game are happening in the real world, forcing him to join the lead character to stop the conspiracy.

468693.title: Territory 8
468693.description: Two scientists confront a deadly cover-up when a chemical weapon explodes in the desert and hostile survivors try to escape the quarantined territory.

468864.title: The Freedom of Silence
468864.description: In the year 2030, America has become a twisted version of freedom. Truth is silenced, and believing in God is considered a terrorist act.

468958.title: A Dark Matter
468958.description: A young artist slips into a surreal realm where he sets out to uncover the disturbing truth about the mysterious disappearance of his girlfriend.

468961.title: Found in Time
468961.description: Life is a puzzle for a psychic who experiences time out of order. A shocking murder plunges him on a race to change both past and present.

469539.title: Brain Dead
469539.description: An experimental operation plunges a brilliant neurosurgeon into a mind-bending nightmare that blurs the line between reality and delusion.

473242.title: Split Second
473242.description: In a futuristic, partially submerged London, a burned-out cop investigates a bizarre series of murders that point to a killer who might not be human.

473503.title: The KAOS Brief
473503.description: Hacked footage reveals the terrifying story of a four Millennials whose lives fall into a rabbit hole after witnessing strange lights in the sky.

474269.title: Cold Zone
474269.description: A man interrupts his family vacation in Alaska to team up with a retired environmental expert and save the world from a flash-freezing storm.

475054.title: Painkillers
475054.description: A squad of US Marines awakens in a hospital with no memories of their mission in Afghanistan, nor the otherworldly artifact they were sent to find.

476641.title: Franklyn
476641.description: Fate, love, and tragedy bind souls who collide in parallel worlds of London and a futuristic city, where a rebel battles a corrupt religious regime.

476704.title: Containment
476704.description: When neighbors in an apartment complex wake up to see they've been sealed inside by strangers in hazmat suits, they start to turn on each other.

478727.title: Pandemic
478727.description: A virus tears through New Mexico. A local veterinarian teams up with an eccentric rancher to expose the true threat and save mankind.

485860.title: The 10th Victim
485860.description: Society's lust for violence is satisfied by "The Big Hunt," an international game of legalized murder. But when the sport's two top assassins are pitted against each other, they find that love is the most dangerous game of all.

487250.title: Aftermath
487250.description: A radioactive world surrounds 9 survivors of a nuclear apocalypse who must choose between a farmhouse shelter or zombie-like creatures outside.

487416.title: Ovnis en Zacapa
487416.description: Un frustrado profesor universitario viaja como reportero sensacionalista de TV a un pueblo de Guatemala donde ha habido varios avistamientos de ovnis.

488345.title: Shark Hunter
488345.description: After a giant shark destroys an entire research station, a man must lead his team of divers to hunt and stop the underwater menace.

488758.title: Patient 62
488758.description: A man tortured by nightmares of his kidnapped stripper sister goes to save her from human trafficking and mutilation, but the nightmares aren't his.

489450.title: Weather Wars
489450.description: Washington haunting series of weather disasters, devastating the city. Two brothers - sons of a recognized scientist and meteorologist - begin an investigation to explain the unexpected attacks of nature.

489702.title: Dark Descent
489702.description: When investigating the mysterious death of a group of underwater miners, a man discovers a dangerous conspiracy that could turn on him next.

490254.title: Hayflick Limit
490254.description: After a woman wakes up in a lab alone, she must escape and figure out the reason why she was selected for a bizarre age experiment.

492257.title: Capsule
492257.description: In the early days of the Space Race, a British astronaut finds himself stranded beyond Earth, and mixed up in a conspiracy he doesn't understand.

493214.title: Flashburn
493214.description: A man who is the only one who knows the cure for a global and deadly virus finds himself sealed off in a warehouse after a car crash with no memory.

495444.title: Loophole
495444.description: Descendants of Judas are hunted down when a violence-inducing genetic code is discovered and thrusts a young woman into an all-out spiritual war.

499235.title: CTRL
499235.description: After a lonely computer programmer creates an AI device that can evolve and adapt, it overtakes his life and threatens to destroy his loved ones.

499281.title: Lunopolis
499281.description: Two documentary filmmakers discover news about the moon, which leads them down a dangerous path with a potentially real conspiracy theory.

499764.title: Resonance
499764.description: A young couple on vacation at a remote destination are stalked by something evil that tries to claim their lives when one of them is mortally injured.

499979.title: The Invasion of Carol Enders
499979.description: A woman who awakes from a coma finds herself possessed by the spirit of a murder victim, who died at the very moment she lost consciousness.

502231.title: Tornados de Hielo (Doblado)
502231.description: Scientists conducting weather experiments unwittingly unleash an onslaught of freezing windstorms and ice tornadoes throughout the Pacific Northwest.

505469.title: Black Hollow Cage
505469.description: Living in a secluded forest home with her father, a young girl discovers a strange black cube that seemingly delivers messages from her future self.

506048.title: Danny's Doomsday
506048.description: When flesh-eating monsters attack suburbia, two teenage brothers are forced to barricade themselves in their basement and learn to get along.

506679.title: New Rose Hotel
506679.description: In the future, two businessmen, who are hired to steal secrets from a rival, enlist the aid of a beautiful and mysterious, but volatile, call girl.

506700.title: Atomic Twister
506700.description: When tornadoes hit a nuclear power plant, catastrophe is unleashed on a small town. Can anyone stop this path of destruction before it’s too late?

507433.title: The Stepford Wives
507433.description: A modern woman and her family, new to the town of Stepford, starts to see that the wives in town are suspiciously perfect and submissive to their men.

515996.title: Replace
515996.description: A young woman with a crippling dermatological disease discovers that to correct her complexion she must replace her skin with that of other girls.

516026.title: Man Vs.
516026.description: TV host Doug Woods is dropped off in the Canadian wilderness to survive one week alone. But he may not be the only one out there...

516028.title: Empathy, Inc.
516028.description: A VR startup offers users the chance to experience a less fortunate life. But one investor is about to discover the company's true nature.

530233.title: The 11th Patient
530233.description: A doctor who specializes in treating trauma patients tries to use virtual reality technology in order to rescue a comatose child and catch a criminal.

531788.title: Beyond the Sky
531788.description: A man who attends UFO conventions to disprove alien abductions meets a woman who is days away from age 28 and claims to be abducted every 7 years.

540054.title: Rupture
540054.description: A single mom tries to break free from a mysterious organization that seeks to expose her to her deepest fear in order to reveal her true self.

540293.title: Apocalypse Kiss
540293.description: In a future world where a government agent hunts for a prolific killer, two mysterious female lovers come to town and the body count begins to rise.

540908.title: The Cyclotron
540908.description: In 1944, memories of love and nuclear physics oppose forces, as an Allied spy sets out to execute a Berlin scientist who knows how to build an A-bomb.

552860.title: Edge of Extinction
552860.description: Years after World War III, a man hides in the countryside. Until a chance meeting brings him back into the twisted world of humanity.

553667.title: Shadowplay
553667.description: When three strangers wake up trapped in a room without doors or windows, they must work together to figure out why they are there and how to escape.

555044.title: Battle of Memories
555044.description: A cutting-edge procedure that can switch a person’s mind with another and clear memories goes wrong for a man who gets the mind of a serial killer.

555622.title: The Directive
555622.description: In a post-apocalyptic future world where most of humanity is wiped out by a virus, a robot promises to reunite a survivor with his family.

557842.title: The Unseen
557842.description: A deadbeat dad returns years later to bond with his troubled daughter. When she goes missing, he must risk it all to find her as he turns invisible.

559203.title: Sinkhole
559203.description: After a massive sinkhole swallows an entire town, a group of teenagers must fight for their lives when their bus becomes trapped underground.

562530.title: Interpreters
562530.description: When the residents of a small community are slowly picked off, the killer’s unusual calling card brings in a former black-ops soldier to investigate.

562731.title: Case 347
562731.description: Psychologist and UFO skeptic Dr. Mia Jansen joins forces with two documentary film makers who set out to prove alien abduction claims are a form of “mass hysteria”, but during their research, unexplainable events begin.

562807.title: Shortwave
562807.description: A couple whose child died enter a phase of terror when the husband’s experimental shortwave device starts distorting his wife’s mind by evil means.

562824.title: Threshold
562824.description: During an apocalyptic event, a couple risks redemption at the hands of an otherworldly intruder who knows details about their tragic past.

567814.title: Rudraksh
567814.description: A day laborer is possessed by a demon out for world rule after he finds a sacred seed, a goal that a healer, his father and a researcher try to end.

569076.title: The Honeymoon Phase
569076.description: For a $50,000 bounty, a young couple becomes guinea pigs in a month-long futuristic experiment that sequesters them from the outside world.

570972.title: Dark Island
570972.description: When a defense contractor loses contact with its bioweapons lab on a remote island, a team of soldiers and scientists is sent to learn what happened.

574336.title: Eternal Code
574336.description: After a CEO and her husband refuse to support new technology that would sustain human life at a highly unethical cost, they are kidnapped.

574353.title: Abejas Asesinas (Doblado)
574353.description: Cuando un camión que transporta un enjambre de abejas se estrella, un pueblo es atacado. Ahora, un sheriff y un abejero deben salvar a los locales.

576722.title: Alien Strain
576722.description: An innocent man suspected of his girlfriend’s vanishing on a camping trip sees her return there alive a year later, but now she is an alien mutant.

577298.title: Omega Code
577298.description: An action-packed struggle for good and evil occurs when cyberwarfare attempts to manipulate the code of Biblical prophecies to start the end of days.

580232.title: Extinction: Patient Zero
580232.description: The clock is ticking, as scientists trapped in a safe room learn if they are infected by a deadly virus and can escape the activated safety protocols.

580375.title: Experiment
580375.description: A man and woman roam the streets of a foreign city with no memories and plagued by nightmarish visions, unaware that dark forces guide their actions.

581059.title: White Chamber
581059.description: In a dystopian post-Brexit Britain, torn apart by civil war, a woman with a questionable past finds herself a captive in a futuristic prison pod.

581329.title: The Caller
581329.description: When a stranger asks a mysterious woman for a favor, a twisted game goes from erotic hints to a tense fear that chillingly explodes in a shock ending.

581969.title: Before the Fire
581969.description: In the midst of a global pandemic, a young woman seeks refuge at her childhood home, only to discover something far more dangerous awaits her there.

581989.title: Listening
581989.description: Grad students invent a telepathy device, but a covert group pits them against each other, in a war over privacy of thought and the fate of free will

585082.title: Paramnesia
585082.description: After waking up on the floor of his apartment with total amnesia, a young man struggles to regain his memory while dodging the two men chasing him.

585644.title: The Sleeper
585644.description: After the government creates an assassin that can enter a person’s dream and kill them, a man tries to stop the murders despite its unstoppable power.

587005.title: Peripheral
587005.description: A writer starts her second novel, but new software wraps her up in a mind control experiment, as she desperately tries to make her deadline.

595462.title: Adrenalin: Fear the Rush
595462.description: The Russian government has collapsed amidst the chaos a terrible weapon has leaked out. Virulent microflage, a deadly germ of the cold war has begun to spread across Eastern Europe, killing massive numbers of people

596184.title: Cita a Ciegas (Doblado)
596184.description: A man goes blind when remembering his lost girlfriend, but the doctors can't find anything wrong with his eyes. They fit him with an experimental device which allows him to see with the aid of a computer interface and brain electrodes. Meanwhile, a taxi driver is taking young women up to their apartments, giving them gas, and performing a little fatal amateur surgery on them. Their paths inevitably converge, and the blind man must try to stop the psychopath.

599230.title: Incarnation
599230.description: A man wakes up on a bench without any idea who he is until he is shot dead by four masked assassins. The man wakes on the same bench thinking his death was a dream until the assassins return and despite his attempts to escape, they kill him again. Stuck in this hellish loop, he tries to unravel the mystery and with each death he gets closer to the truth.

606642.title: Survival Games
606642.description: In the near future, a group of contestants play a televised game in Russia where those voted off must conquer their worst fears or die trying.

606891.title: The Arbors
606891.description: A lonely man's life begins to fracture and break after he finds a small creature that bonds with him and carries out his heart’s darkest wishes.

610134.title: Alien Agenda Project Grey
610134.description: A psychiatrist listens to her criminally insane patient, as he recounts the story of the murder of his friends, which might involve alien forces.

610618.title: Trinity
610618.description: Betrayal and deep twists occur when a genetic scientist, indicted for crimes against humanity, tells two investigators that he’s an engineered clone.

619748.title: A Breath Away
619748.description: When a deadly fog engulfs Paris, a pair of concerned parents risk everything to find their daughter, who is trapped in a medical tank.

620724.title: The Complex: Lockdown
620724.description: In the wake of a bioweapons attack in London, two scientists find themselves in lockdown with the suspect as assassins infiltrate their laboratory.

622224.title: River
622224.description: A woman with a troubled past can’t escape the appeal of a scenic and isolating self-journey, but her path is filled with a series of nightmares.

622272.title: Lockdown: 2025
622272.description: When a highly contagious virus puts the entire country on lockdown, enforced by martial law, one family learns they’re not safe in their own home.

623289.title: Channeling
623289.description: In a not-too-distant future where people broadcast online every moment of their lives, a soldier on leave investigates his brother’s suspicious death.

624780.title: Apocalypse of Ice
624780.description: With a pandemic already underway, a scientist with the key to human survival has to survive a devastating polar vortex that has overtaken the globe.

628148.title: Doctor Mabuse
628148.description: When criminal mastermind Dr. Mabuse returns from exile to live out his carefully planned doctrine of terror, only a young detective stands in his way.

629802.title: The Coming
629802.description: An end-of-days thriller about a group of young friends who must use The Book to get through a vivid and destructive implosion of life as we know it.

630370.title: Sender
630370.description: The discovery on a remote island of an amnesiac woman and her increasingly impressive psychic powers kicks off a bloody international race to find her.

631171.title: Paradise Lost
631171.description: A thriller about the deep Central America rain forest that a team of dedicated scientists must try to keep from being deforested with chemical sprays.

631173.title: Mind Storm
631173.description: “Sharknado” star Ian Ziering plays a married video game programmer who is unaware that his employer is embedding mind control messages in the apps.

631544.title: Monsters of Man
631544.description: An illegal U.S. military op goes awry when killer robots are unleashed on heroin producers in Southeast Asia and end up wiping out an entire village.

631954.title: Buoyancy
631954.description: A sociology major with an online channel takes a days-long submarine tour with a wealthy tech mogul whose invitation is more sinister than she knows.

633142.title: The Removals
633142.description: A pair of agents works to undermine their own employer in this dramatic analogy for the result of social communication in the modern world.

633199.title: Trakked
633199.description: When a young woman suspects her boyfriend is being unfaithful, she implants a camera inside his head that allows her to track every alterous move.

636640.title: 3 Days on the Cross
636640.description: In the post-apocalyptic wasteland of the Texas desert, two men inside a bunker with an unknown motive, surveil a man searching for his missing daughter.

639804.title: The Wave
639804.description: When an insurance lawyer goes out on the town with his friend to celebrate a promotion, he is dosed with a hallucinogen that changes his life forever.

640130.title: Entombed
640130.description: After a pandemic destroys the last of an already delicate civilization, a man ventures out to find shelter in a world filled with danger.

646735.title: The Chain Reaction
646735.description: A chance meeting with a scientist turns a pair of tourists in the central Australian countryside into the targets of a nuclear facility’s assassins.

648137.title: Before I'm Dead
648137.description: In the wake of his wife’s death, a grieving young man slowly succumbs to agoraphobia until the laws of time and space begin to unravel around him.

648545.title: Mind Talker
648545.description: A head injury bestows a detective with sudden powers of telepathy that send him down a mysterious path to uncover a new mystery in unknown territory.

649963.title: Freaks
649963.description: A little girl who has been shut away from the outside world by her father soon discovers a dangerous universe awaiting beyond her front door.

652228.title: Ice
652228.description: After a planet hits the sun and causes an ice age, a group of survivors band together to find the only habitable land left on the planet.

658933.title: Infrared Dreams
658933.description: In the future, a captive woman undergoes psychological and emotional testing by her abductor while learning that he may not be her biggest concern.

659745.title: The President's Staff
659745.description: The president, an intern, and two technicians find themselves trapped in the Oval Office after discovering that the exits have been wired with bombs.

661451.title: Sensation
661451.description: Inducted into a secret superhuman DNA program, a postman learns that he'll be able to receive, control, and send information based on others' senses.

668090.title: Incontrol
668090.description: College kids develop a machine that projects their consciousness onto others, allowing them to live inside their rich and beautiful fellow students.

672034.title: That Cold Dead Look in Your Eyes
672034.description: Leonard is having strange hallucinations. Is it an aftereffect of new technology? He must figure it out before being trapped in this torment forever.

672464.title: Godsend
672464.description: When their eight-year-old son dies, a grieving couple turns to an enigmatic geneticist who successfully clones their child—with terrifying results.

676667.title: Elizabeth Harvest
676667.description: A young wife is drawn into her wealthy husband's twisted world of secret human cloning in this brain-bending plunge into our darkest desires.

677018.title: Only
677018.description: After a comet releases a mysterious plague threatening to kill all women on the planet, a couple is put to the ultimate test as they try to survive.

677232.title: The Great Awakening
677232.description: The world of a young couple is turned upside down when Lindsay’s sudden nightmares and hallucinations begin to unearth an unexpected truth.

679344.title: Driver 113
679344.description: Driver 113 liked his job for Mappr360, mapping America's forgotten roads until his cameras captured something his eyes were not meant to see.

680718.title: Fireball
680718.description: Inspector Ava Williams investigates a prison fire and traces it to its source: an inmate seeking revenge against those who put him behind bars.

682175.title: Stonados
682175.description: When an unprecedented weather event puts the Eastern Seaboard under siege, a former storm chaser’s untested theory is the only chance of stopping it.

684144.title: Devil's Gate
684144.description: While investigating a woman's disappearance, an FBI agent encounters an unholy force locked away in a booby-trapped, middle-of-nowhere farmhouse.

685612.title: Kultur Shock!
685612.description: Three amnesiac American immigrants are tortured by an Uncle Sam doll in a locked, windowless room in this strange, subversive satire.

686221.title: Firequake
686221.description: An introduction to Helios, a revolutionary clean coal energy source so powerful it rivals the force of the sun and will solve the energy crisis.

686327.title: Harmony
686327.description: A wounded soldier begins to suspect the military medical facility where she’s been placed isn’t for her recovery, but for something sinister.

687555.title: The Call Up
687555.description: A group of online gamers invited to participate in a state-of-the-art virtual reality game find themselves trapped inside a real-life shoot ‘em up.

688214.title: The Ghost Lights
688214.description: Upon discovering a tape describing strange disappearances and mysterious lights, a journalist goes on a road trip across Texas to discover the truth.

693778.title: Novia Cibernética (Doblado)
693778.description: Después de la muerte de su esposa, Rick se topa con la web oscura después de enterarse de que la esposa de su vecino es en realidad un cyborg.

698078.title: Apollo 18
698078.description: Decades-old found footage involving three astronauts and an abandoned, secret NASA mission reveals why the U.S. has never returned to the moon.

698917.title: The Night Visitor
698917.description: When a couple hires a spiritualist to help with their marriage, her advice to record their lives reveals an entity in conversations with their son.

698959.title: Repo Men
698959.description: After being outfitted with a top-of-the-line heart replacement, an organ repo man must go on the run when he finds himself unable to pay for it.

702589.title: Dawn
702589.description: An unsuspecting couple gets into a rideshare only to find out that the driver is deranged, and they now have to fight for their lives.

702914.title: Absolon
702914.description: In a world ravaged by a deadly virus and wholly dependent on a single pharmaceutical for survival, the man who may have found a cure is murdered.

703581.title: Zona Mortal (Doblado)
703581.description: Mientras busca ayuda después de un accidente, un hombre descubre que cualquier ser vivo dentro de un radio de 50 pies de él morirá instantáneamente.

704017.title: Deleted
704017.description: A lonely introvert begins to suspect he's nothing more than a fake social media account and sets out to find his creator before he's deleted forever.

704490.title: The Last Survivors
704490.description: In the near future when society collapses and water becomes scarce, 17-year-old Kendal fights a violent water baron’s henchmen to keep a well open.

707525.title: Cerebrum
707525.description: A sizable sum of money convinces Tom to become his estranged father’s lab rat in a memory transfer study when he commits a crime he can’t remember.

707535.title: Destination Marfa
707535.description: A road trip becomes a nightmare when four lifelong friends take a fateful shortcut through the small, peculiar West Texas town of Marfa.

707589.title: Synapse
707589.description: A memory dealer finds himself on the run from federal narcotics agents determined to keep the secrets in his mind hidden from the world forever.

708086.title: Meander
708086.description: After accepting a ride from a mysterious stranger, Lisa wakes up in a labyrinthian series of strange tubes full of deadly traps at every turn.

709943.title: Incident at Montauk
709943.description: Jed Logan comes to discover his UFO sighting may be linked to a secret government project which leads him down a dangerous path to uncover the truth.

711152.title: Dark Winter
711152.description: Fearing for the safety of their children, two parents embark on a dangerous mission against the great evil that is the council of Ashton Falls.

711266.title: The Ant Farm
711266.description: A couple’s peaceful remote retreat is interrupted by the discovery on a frozen lake of a scientist’s comatose daughter who’s tangled in a conspiracy.

712853.title: The Moment After
712853.description: After a mass disappearance, two FBI agents are called in to investigate the strange occurrence, which may hold religious significance.

714354.title: The Astronaut's Wife
714354.description: After briefly losing consciousness during a space mission, an astronaut returns home as a chilling reality begins to set in for his doting wife.

714665.title: Looker
714665.description: To clear his name in the deaths of three commercial actresses, a Beverly Hills plastic surgeon chases clues that lead him to a global conglomerate.

722364.title: Absolute Zero
722364.description: After a shift in the Earth's polarity, one scientist races against time to stop Miami from being plunged into total darkness and -460 degree weather.

722520.title: Toxina (Doblado)
722520.description: Un thriller sobre un conocido científico que es reclutado por una compañía farmacéutica para ayudar a desarrollar una vacuna contra un virus mortal.

723249.title: What Lies Below
723249.description: Liberty returns from camp to an introduction by her mother’s fiancé, whose charm and beauty paint the picture of a man too perfect to be human.

725368.title: Let's Be Evil
725368.description: A desperate young woman takes a job at a school for gifted children only to be thrust into a virtual nightmare that forces her to fight for her life.

726060.title: Furia De Dragón (Doblado)
726060.description: Durante una excursión para descubrir nuevas especies, un equipo de investigadores se adentran en las montañas y se topan con una peligrosa criatura.

100000333.title: Errors of the Human Body
100000333.description: An intense sci-fi thriller about a brilliant geneticist who, while working on a top-secret project, unwittingly unleashes a new virus.

100000685.title: The Last Days
100000685.description: As a mysterious epidemic spreads across the planet trapping humanity indoors, one man sets off on a dangerous quest to save his missing girlfriend.

100000766.title: Residents of Arcadia
100000766.description: During a party, two influencers discover a ticking clock throughout their home, dreading what awaits them as the countdown approaches zero.

100001043.title: Entidad De Identificación De Llamadas (Doblado)
